<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<h3>Travel information</h3>
    The Travel Response Centre has brought together all of Durham County Council’s demand responsive transport services into one easy booking system using just one telephone number: 0191 383 5 383. More details are available on the transport website (link below). From April 2006, the national requirement is that there will be free bus travel in local areas for people over 60 or people with disability. For further information contact Durham County Council on 0191 383 3337.


</div>
